#### [NEW] [persona.py](file:///c:/Onedrive/OneDrive%20-%20University%20of%20Southern%20California/Desktop/Job%20Hunting/Ditto-Synthetic-Matchmaking-Feedback-Loop-Simulator/src/models/persona.py)
