### Ditto Bot (Matchmaking Agent)

#### [NEW] [ditto_bot/agent.py](file:///c:/Onedrive/OneDrive%20-%20University%20of%20Southern%20California/Desktop/Job%20Hunting/Ditto-Synthetic-Matchmaking-Feedback-Loop-Simulator/src/ditto_bot/agent.py)
- Stateful conversational agent managing the matchmaking flow
- State: `preference_history`, `rejection_reasons`, `shown_matches`, `current_round`
- Flow: collect preferences → present match → handle accept/reject → propose date → collect feedback → offer rematch

#### [NEW] [ditto_bot/matcher.py](file:///c:/Onedrive/OneDrive%20-%20University%20of%20Southern%20California/Desktop/Job%20Hunting/Ditto-Synthetic-Matchmaking-Feedback-Loop-Simulator/src/ditto_bot/matcher.py)
- `MatchScorer` class with hybrid scoring: embedding cosine similarity (0.4 weight) + LLM compatibility reasoning (0.6 weight)
- Candidate filtering (exclude shown matches, apply hard preferences)
- Returns top match with natural-language justification

#### [NEW] [ditto_bot/prompts.py](file:///c:/Onedrive/OneDrive%20-%20University%20of%20Southern%20California/Desktop/Job%20Hunting/Ditto-Synthetic-Matchmaking-Feedback-Loop-Simulator/src/ditto_bot/prompts.py)
- System prompt for Ditto Bot (friendly, professional matchmaker persona)
- Match presentation template, rejection handling prompt, date proposal prompt

---

### Customer Bot (User Bot)

